## 3. TTIS Field App

A **standalone native app** (`H:\Projects\ttis-field-app`, Expo `~54` / React Native, iOS+Android) —
**not** a browser page. Per ADR‑0001 a native app was chosen over PWA for reliable push (P1 safety
alerts) and durable on‑device storage of unsynced DCAA timecards. Crews use the installed app; it is
a thin client over the **same VBS API** (`https://app.tti-solutions.com`, set in `app.json` →
`extra.apiBaseUrl`). Scope doc: `ttis-ai/docs/MOBILE_FIELD_APP_SCOPE.md`.

### 3.1 Setup & run (dev)

```powershell
cd H:\Projects\ttis-field-app
npm install
npm run start                # Expo dev server + QR (open in Expo Go)
npm run ios                  # iOS simulator
npm run android              # Android emulator
npm run web                  # react-native-web preview
```

### 3.2 What a field user gets

- **Login** with VBS credentials (`field_crew` role); JWT stored in `expo-secure-store` (Keychain/Keystore).
- **Tabs:** Home, Time, Schedule, Pay, Assistant (FIELDAIDE — a read‑only field agent).
- **Submit forms:** timecard, daily log, incident (with tappable body‑map), travel — all exactly‑once
  (Idempotency‑Key). All reads are server‑scoped to the caller's `user_id` (a tech only sees their own).
- **Backend endpoints:** `/api/v1/timecards/summary`, `/api/v1/payroll/next-payday`,
  `/api/v1/schedule/me`, `/api/v1/field/assistant`, `/api/v1/projects/assigned`, plus the standard
  `/timecards`, `/daily-logs`, `/incidents`, `/travel/requests` submits.

### 3.3 Build & distribute (EAS)

```powershell
npm install -g eas-cli
eas login
eas build --platform ios       # → TestFlight
eas build --platform android   # → Play Internal Testing
eas update                     # OTA JS update (expo-updates)
```

> Status: P0 (auth + tab shell + live data) and P1 (submit forms) shipped. Pending: P3 push
> (device registry + mission‑critical inbox) and P4 hardening (offline queue, biometric unlock, EAS pilot).

### 3.4 Troubleshoot

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| Can't reach API in dev | pointing at prod by default | App uses `app.tti-solutions.com`; for local VBS, override `extra.apiBaseUrl` / `lib/config.ts`. |
| Login fails | VBS down or wrong role | Verify VBS health; user must have `field_crew` role. |
| Expo Go won't connect | phone/PC not same LAN | Same network, or use a tunnel (`expo start --tunnel`). |

